**Reconciliation report:** `examples/reconciliation_001.md.sample`

This sample gates the auth-provider refactor plan from `examples/plan.yml.sample`.
The reconciler sample is not fully content-aligned with that plan, but it does
establish the key teaching signal: one compatibility-sensitive task still needs
either a retry or an explicit operator override.

